{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.01.020 Repeal of Prior Inconsistent Ordinances Any and all ordinances or portions thereof heretofore enacted by the Tribal Council which are in any way conflict with the provisions of this Civil and Criminal Code are hereby repealed. Prior Codifications \u00a71.01.020 was formerly codified as 101.2", "num": "1.01.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.01|1.01.020", "title": "1.01.020 Repeal of Prior Inconsistent Ordinances", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.01.020"}
