{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.01.030 Interpretation of This Code This Code shall be interpreted pursuant to the customs and traditions of the Bad River Band of Lake Superior Tribe of Chippewa Indians. Where any doubt arises as to these customs and traditions, the Court may request the advice of counselors familiar with these customs and traditions. If none such exist, then the Court may use appropriate Federal or State law as guidelines. Prior Codifications \u00a71.01.030 was formerly codified as 101.3", "num": "1.01.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.01|1.01.030", "title": "1.01.030 Interpretation of This Code", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.01.030"}
