{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.01.040 Severability Clause Should any section of this Civil and Criminal Code be determined as unconstitutional by any court of proper jurisdiction, that determination shall not affect any other provisions of this Civil and Criminal Code. Prior Codifications \u00a71.01.040 was formerly codified as 101.4", "num": "1.01.040", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.01|1.01.040", "title": "1.01.040 Severability Clause", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.01.040"}
