{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.01.050 Future Amendments of the Court Code This Court Code may be amended by ordinance of the Tribal Council and any amendments adopted shall be effective and become part of this Code as provided in the amending ordinance, subject however to review by the Secretary of the Interior as provided in Article VI, Sec. 1(g) of the Bad River Tribal Constitution . Prior Codifications \u00a71.01.050 was formerly codified as 101.5", "num": "1.01.050", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.01|1.01.050", "title": "1.01.050 Future Amendments of the Court Code", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.01.050"}
