{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. Chapter 1.03 Establishment and Duties 1.03.010 1.03.020 1.03.030 1.03.040 1.03.050 1.03.060 1.03.070 1.03.080 1.03.090 1.03.100", "num": "1.03", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03", "title": "Chapter 1.03 Establishment and Duties", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.010", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.010 The Tribal Council hereby establishes a Tribal Court which shall have jurisdiction as provided by Section 106 or other applicable tribal law. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.010 was formerly codified as 103.1", "num": "1.03.010", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.010", "title": "1.03.010", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.010"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.020", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.020 Anyone entering the Bad River Reservation consents to the jurisdiction of the Bad River Tribal Court. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.020 was formerly codified as 103.2", "num": "1.03.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.020", "title": "1.03.020", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.020"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.030", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.030 The Court shall consist of one chief judge to be selected by the Tribal Council and such associate judges as the Council may deem necessary. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.030 was formerly codified as 103.3", "num": "1.03.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.030", "title": "1.03.030", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.030"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.040", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.040 All penalties and forfeitures assessed shall be in accordance with the provisions adopted in this code. In no case, however, shall a fine exceed $5,000.00 or a term of incarceration exceed one year for each violation. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.040 was formerly codified as 103.4", "num": "1.03.040", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.040", "title": "1.03.040", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.040"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.050", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.050 The Court will convene at such location and at such times as shall be designated by the Court. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.050 was formerly codified as 103.5", "num": "1.03.050", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.050", "title": "1.03.050", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.050"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.060", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.060 The Court shall collect all fines, forfeitures and other monies generated through enforcement of Tribal Ordinances. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.060 was formerly codified as 103.6", "num": "1.03.060", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.060", "title": "1.03.060", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.060"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.070", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.070 All receipts shall be disposed of as prescribed by Tribal Council. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.070 was formerly codified as 103.7", "num": "1.03.070", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.070", "title": "1.03.070", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.070"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.080", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.080 Court personnel shall be selected under standards established by the Tribal Council. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.080 was formerly codified as 103.8", "num": "1.03.080", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.080", "title": "1.03.080", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.080"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.090", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.090 A Court of Appeals is hereby established, consisting of the judges of other tribal courts who from time to time consent to sit on a panel of three judges to hear appeals cases. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.090 was formerly codified as 103.9", "num": "1.03.090", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.090", "title": "1.03.090", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.090"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.100", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.03.100 A Court of Appeals panel, consisting of three judges, shall be selected by the Clerk of the Court of Appeals upon the proper filing of appeal. Prior Codifications \u00a71.03.100 was formerly codified as 103.10", "num": "1.03.100", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.03|1.03.100", "title": "1.03.100", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.03.100"}
