{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.24.140 Removal of Tenant on Termination of Tenancy If a tenant remains in possession without consent of the landlord after termination of his tenancy, the landlord may in every case proceed in any manner permitted by law to remove the tenant and recover damages for such holding over. Prior Codifications \u00a71.24.140 was formerly codified as 124.14", "num": "1.24.140", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.24|1.24.140", "title": "1.24.140 Removal of Tenant on Termination of Tenancy", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.24.140"}
