{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.24.250 Appeal Appeals may be taken only as provided under Chapter 1.21 , except that notice of appeal under Section 1.21.090 must be filed within 15 days of the entry of judgment or order for writ of restitution appealed from. No stay of the judgment or writ of restitution may be granted to the defendant under Section 1.21.100(d) unless security for all rents, costs, and fees due, and all rent to be due during the pendency of the appeal is provided upon terms acceptable to the court. Prior Codifications \u00a71.24.250 was formerly codified as 124.25", "num": "1.24.250", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.24|1.24.250", "title": "1.24.250 Appeal", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.24.250"}
