{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.28.010 Jurisdiction in Tribal Court Pursuant to the Bad River Tribal Constitution , Article VI Sections 1 (j) and (q) , the Tribal Court shall have jurisdiction over all petitions for adult guardianship. A guardianship of the estate of any adult person, once granted shall extend to wherever any of his or her assets, whatever the nature, are located. Prior Codifications \u00a71.28.010 was formerly codified as 128.01", "num": "1.28.010", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.28|1.28.010", "title": "1.28.010 Jurisdiction in Tribal Court", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.28.010"}
