{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 1.29.080 Modifications Any order issued under this chapter may be modified upon motion, notice, and hearing. Prior Codifications \u00a71.29.080 was formerly codified as 129.08", "num": "1.29.080", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.29|1.29.080", "title": "1.29.080 Modifications", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.29.080"}
