{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. Chapter 1.43 Rules of Evidence; Judicial Notice 1.43.010 Adjudicative Facts 1.43.020 Foreign Law 1.43.030 Legislative Facts", "num": "1.43", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|1|1.43", "title": "Chapter 1.43 Rules of Evidence; Judicial Notice", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/1.43"}
