{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.02.030 Hunting Prescribed (a) No person shall hunt or take any deer within the reservation except during the open season. (b) No person shall hunt or take any deer within the reservation in excess of the limit allowed. ( 9-2-81-12 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.02.030 was formerly codified as 301.3", "num": "3.02.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.02|3.02.030", "title": "3.02.030 Hunting Prescribed", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.02.030"}
