{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.02.090 Seizure and Forfeiture (a) Any deer taken in violation of this chapter may be seized by the Conservation Department and may be ordered forfeited. (b) Any equipment used in the violation of this chapter maybe seized by the Conservation Department and ordered forfeited. ( 9-2-81-12 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.02.090 was formerly codified as 301.9", "num": "3.02.090", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.02|3.02.090", "title": "3.02.090 Seizure and Forfeiture", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.02.090"}
