{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.03.030 Fishing Prescribed (a) No person shall fish for or take any walleye within the reservation except during the open season. (b) No person shall fish for or take any walleye within the reservation in excess of the limit allowed. ( 9-2-81-12 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.03.030 was formerly codified as 302.3", "num": "3.03.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.03|3.03.030", "title": "3.03.030 Fishing Prescribed", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.03.030"}
