{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.03.040 Season, Limits Open seasons and limits are established as follows: (a) Member. In the Kakagon River system the open season shall be at all times other than those posted by the Conservation Department at spawning season. In the Bad River system the open season shall be year-round. There shall be no limit. (b) Non-member. There shall be no open season in either the Kakagon or Bad River systems. ( 9-2-81-12 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.03.040 was formerly codified as 302.4", "num": "3.03.040", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.03|3.03.040", "title": "3.03.040 Season, Limits", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.03.040"}
