{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.10.020 Penalties (a) Any individual who violates this ordinance shall be assessed a civil forfeiture of not more than $100.00. (b) Any individual who violates this ordinance and who has once previously been found in violation of this ordinance shall be assessed a civil forfeiture of not more than $250.00. (c) Any individual who violates this ordinance and who has more than once previously been found in violation of this ordinance shall be assessed a civil forfeiture of not more than $500.00. Prior Codifications \u00a73.10.020 was formerly codified as 320.2", "num": "3.10.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.10|3.10.020", "title": "3.10.020 Penalties", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.10.020"}
