{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.11.010 Ordinance Title This ordinance shall be known, and may be cited as, the BAD RIVER RESERVATION WETLAND AND WATERCOURSE PROTECTION ORDINANCE. ( 12-16-09-138 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.11.010 was formerly codified as 323.1", "num": "3.11.010", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.11|3.11.010", "title": "3.11.010 Ordinance Title", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.11.010"}
