{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.14.040 Interpretation The provisions of this ordinance shall be interpreted and applied as minimum requirements applicable to tribal members, and shall be liberally construed in favor of the Tribe. The provisions shall not, however, be deemed a limitation or repeal of any other tribal power or authority. ( 1-10-07-14 ; 1-18-91-161 ; 5-8-85-179 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.14.040 was formerly codified as 326.04", "num": "3.14.040", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.14|3.14.040", "title": "3.14.040 Interpretation", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.14.040"}
