{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.14.150 Non-Commercial Species No member may sell any fish of the following species: rainbow (steelhead) trout, brook trout, or sturgeon. ( 1-10-07-14 ; 1-18-91-161 ; 5-8-85-179 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.14.150 was formerly codified as 326.15", "num": "3.14.150", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.14|3.14.150", "title": "3.14.150 Non-Commercial Species", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.14.150"}
