{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.14.170 Deputization Conservation wardens of the Great Lakes Indian Fish and Wildlife Commission are hereby deputized by the Tribal Council to enforce the terms of this ordinance against members. ( 1-10-07-14 ; 1-18-91-161 ; 5-8-85-179 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.14.170 was formerly codified as 326.17", "num": "3.14.170", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.14|3.14.170", "title": "3.14.170 Deputization", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.14.170"}
