{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.14.190 Tribal Court The Tribal Court is hereby authorized to adjudicate all matters arising under this ordinance, pursuant to the provisions of the Tribal Court Code. ( 1-10-07-14 ; 1-18-91-161 ; 5-8-85-179 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.14.190 was formerly codified as 326.19", "num": "3.14.190", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.14|3.14.190", "title": "3.14.190 Tribal Court", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.14.190"}
