{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.14.220 Collection of Money Penalties Enforcement of the penalties imposed by Section 3.14.200, Section 3.14.210(a), or Section 3.14.210(c) of this ordinance may be had through the collection of penalties from funds of the violator held by the Tribe, through the imposition of community service work requirements in lieu of money payment, through debt collection mechanisms of courts of other jurisdictions or through any other method authorized by tribal ordinance or state law. ( 1-10-07-14 ; 1-18-91-161 ; 5-8-85-179 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.14.220 was formerly codified as 326.22", "num": "3.14.220", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.14|3.14.220", "title": "3.14.220 Collection of Money Penalties", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.14.220"}
