{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.14.230 Jurisdiction This tribal court shall have jurisdiction (a) to determine the validity of this chapter , and (b) over any action arising from the implementation of this chapter . ( 1-10-07-14 ; 1-18-91-161 ; 5-8-85-179 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.14.230 was formerly codified as 326.23", "num": "3.14.230", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.14|3.14.230", "title": "3.14.230 Jurisdiction", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.14.230"}
