{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.15.110 Fire Extinguishers Required Coast Guard approved fire extinguishers that must be serviceable condition are: Less Than 26 Feet Long 1 B-I portable Exception None required for vessels less than 26 feet long flammable gases or vapors cannot be trapped in the boat (such as with an open boat and outboard motor. 26 Feet to Less Than 40 Feet Long 2 B-I portables or 1 B-II portable 40 Feet or Longer 3 B-1 portables or 1 B-II portable and 1 B-I portable Prior Codifications \u00a73.15.110 was formerly codified as 327.11", "num": "3.15.110", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.15|3.15.110", "title": "3.15.110 Fire Extinguishers", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.15.110"}
