{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.16.040 Prohibition No member shall assist, encourage or accompany any non-Indian with hunting, fishing, ricing or trapping on trust land within the exterior boundaries of the Bad River Reservation. ( 2-5-86-2 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.16.040 was formerly codified as 330.5", "num": "3.16.040", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.16|3.16.040", "title": "3.16.040 Prohibition", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.16.040"}
