{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.16.050 Penalty (a) The penalty for a violation of any provision of this ordinance shall be (1) a forfeiture not to exceed $500.00; or (2) community service to be set by the court; or (3) both (a) and (b) above. ( 2-5-86-2 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.16.050 was formerly codified as 330.6", "num": "3.16.050", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.16|3.16.050", "title": "3.16.050 Penalty", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.16.050"}
