{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.21.270 Neither the imposition of a penalty as provided for above, nor satisfaction of the terms of such penalty, shall constitute a waiver or release from any additional civil or criminal liabilities, including but not limited to liability for damages to natural resources. Prior Codifications \u00a73.21.270 was formerly codified as 352.10.3", "num": "3.21.270", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.21|3.21.270", "title": "3.21.270", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.21.270"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.21.280", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.21.280 To State of Wisconsin Pursuant to the Tribe's ATV Reciprocal Registration Agreement with the State of Wisconsin, the Department shall on the first working day of each month, or more frequently, supply copies of all registration certificates, including renewals, and changes of address and transfers to the Wisconsin Department of Natural Resources, and the Wisconsin Department of Transportation and the Ashland County Sheriff's Department. Each such agency shall receive current registration information upon request made to the Department. Prior Codifications \u00a73.21.280 was formerly codified as 352.11.1", "num": "3.21.280", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.21|3.21.280", "title": "3.21.280 To State of Wisconsin", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.21.280"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.21.290", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.21.290 To the Applicant The Department shall provide to any qualifying applicant who properly completes a registration application and pays the fee required, a receipt of approved application to be used as proof of registration pending delivery to the applicant of the registration and registration decals. Prior Codifications \u00a73.21.290 was formerly codified as 352.11.2", "num": "3.21.290", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.21|3.21.290", "title": "3.21.290 To the Applicant", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.21.290"}
