{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.22.110 Parents The parent or legal guardian of a minor is financially and legally liable for every act of the minor in violation of this section. ( 6-25-99-300 ; 2-23-99-248 ; 6-18-96-20 ; 8-05-92-142 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.22.110 was formerly codified as 360.11", "num": "3.22.110", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.22|3.22.110", "title": "3.22.110 Parents", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.22.110"}
