{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.22.120 Liability Animal control officers and persons authorized to enforce the provisions of this section shall, in the performance of their official duties, be exempt from any and all liability for acts done or property destroyed by authority of the law. ( 6-25-99-300 ; 2-23-99-248 ; 6-18-96-20 ; 8-05-92-142 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.22.120 was formerly codified as 360.12", "num": "3.22.120", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.22|3.22.120", "title": "3.22.120 Liability", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.22.120"}
