{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.23.030 Applicability This chapter applies to the activities on the Bad River Reservation of members and non-members of the Tribe, and residents and non-residents of the Reservation. ( 6-13-00-425 ; 10-5-90-146 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.23.030 was formerly codified as 375.3", "num": "3.23.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.23|3.23.030", "title": "3.23.030 Applicability", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.23.030"}
