{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.23.090 Administrator (a) The Solid Waste Administrator shall be responsible for the administration of this chapter and of any tribal solid waste collection facilities or systems. (b) This chapter is effective upon passage by the Tribal Council, posting on the Reservation, and publication in the Ashland Daily Press. ( 6-13-00-425 ; 10-5-90-146 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.23.090 was formerly codified as 375.9", "num": "3.23.090", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.23|3.23.090", "title": "3.23.090 Administrator", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.23.090"}
