{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 3.25.030 Adoption and Amendment (a) This law is adopted by the Bad River Tribal Council by resolution 4-1-15-399 and is effective April 1, 2015 . (b) This law may be amended pursuant to the procedures set out in Tribal law by the Bad River Tribal Council. ( 4-1-15-399 .) Prior Codifications \u00a73.25.030 was formerly codified as 380.3", "num": "3.25.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|3|3.25|3.25.030", "title": "3.25.030 Adoption and Amendment", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/3.25.030"}
