{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.01.020 Authority The Tribal Council enacts this Ordinance pursuant to its inherent sovereign authority and its authority under Art. VI, Sections 1 (j) , and (s) of the Tribe's Constitution . ( 5-15-18-1029 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.01.020 was formerly codified as 401.2", "num": "4.01.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.01|4.01.020", "title": "4.01.020 Authority", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.01.020"}
