{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.01.060 Separate Acts of Trespass A separate violation of this ordinance is committed with respect to each parcel of land on which a trespass is committed under Sections 201 and 202. ( 5-15-18-1029 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.01.060 was formerly codified as 401.6", "num": "4.01.060", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.01|4.01.060", "title": "4.01.060 Separate Acts of Trespass", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.01.060"}
