{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.01.090 Jurisdiction The Tribal Court shall have exclusive jurisdiction to enforce this ordinance. ( 5-15-18-1029 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.01.090 was formerly codified as 401.9", "num": "4.01.090", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.01|4.01.090", "title": "4.01.090 Jurisdiction", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.01.090"}
