{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.02.050 Administrator's Duties The administrator of this chapter shall be responsible for assisting applicants with applications, for making all necessary inter-departmental and inter-agency contracts with regard to particular applications, for certifying to the Tribal Council or denying all lease applications based on the standards provided in this chapter , for maintaining the Official Lease Map, and for executing all other tasks specifically assigned to him by this chapter . ( 6-2-82-88 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.02.050 was formerly codified as 403.5", "num": "4.02.050", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.02|4.02.050", "title": "4.02.050 Administrator's Duties", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.02.050"}
