{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.02.100 Application Form The application form attached to this chapter as Appendix B shall be the official application form for residential leases for tribal members. The application form may be modified by the administrator provided such modification is submitted to the Tribal Council for review at the next subsequent regular Tribal Council meeting. ( 6-2-82-88 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.02.100 was formerly codified as 403.10", "num": "4.02.100", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.02|4.02.100", "title": "4.02.100 Application Form", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.02.100"}
