{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.03.010 Purpose The purpose of the Bad River Utility Department will be to manage, operate, and maintain utility systems of the Bad River Indian Tribe. ( 4-4-01-76 ; 5-7-86-28 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.03.010 was formerly codified as 405.1", "num": "4.03.010", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.03|4.03.010", "title": "4.03.010 Purpose", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.03.010"}
