{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.03.020 Place of Business The Utility Department will maintain an office in New Odanah, Wisconsin. It's address will be: Bad River Utility Department P.O. Box 39 Odanah, WI 54861 ( 4-4-01-76 ; 5-7-86-28 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.03.020 was formerly codified as 405.2", "num": "4.03.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.03|4.03.020", "title": "4.03.020 Place of Business", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.03.020"}
