{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.03.080 Enforcement (a) The Utility Department is hereby authorized by the Bad River Tribal Council to shut off services for non-payment. (b) The Utility Department shall enforce its regulations and fee collections by shutting off water services and any and all violators and delinquent bill-payers. The Utility Department shall not seek to attach customer's property, nor seek to have fines assessed by Tribal Court, except in limited cases of blatant or continued abuses or destruction of property. ( 4-4-01-76 ; 5-7-86-28 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.03.080 was formerly codified as 405.8", "num": "4.03.080", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.03|4.03.080", "title": "4.03.080 Enforcement", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.03.080"}
