{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.03.140 Emergency Plan The Utility Department shall develop and maintain an Emergency Plan for the Bad River Water/Wastewater System. The most recent copies of the Emergency Plan shall be maintained at the Utilities Department, the Tribal Operations Manager, the Bad River Fire Department, and the Bad River Police Department. ( 4-4-01-76 ; 5-7-86-28 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.03.140 was formerly codified as 405.14", "num": "4.03.140", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.03|4.03.140", "title": "4.03.140 Emergency Plan", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.03.140"}
