{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.03.150 Amendments or Revisions The Plan of Operation may be amended by a simple majority of Tribal Council members in attendance at a meeting called for that, purpose and thereafter by the Bad River Tribal Council as provided by law. ( 4-4-01-76 ; 5-7-86-28 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.03.150 was formerly codified as 405.15", "num": "4.03.150", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.03|4.03.150", "title": "4.03.150 Amendments or Revisions", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.03.150"}
