{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.06.080 Effective Date and Severability (a) Effective Date . This Ordinance shall be effective upon the date of adoption by resolution of the Bad River Tribal Council, until amended or otherwise expressly invalidated by the Tribal Council. (b) Severability . If the Bad River Tribal Court judges any section, provision, or portion of this Ordinance unconstitutional or invalid, the remainder of this Ordinance shall not affected. Prior Codifications \u00a74.06.080 was formerly codified as 421.8", "num": "4.06.080", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.06|4.06.080", "title": "4.06.080 Effective Date and Severability", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.06.080"}
