{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.09.100 No Merger of Estates There shall be no merger of estates by reason of the execution of a Lease or a Leasehold Mortgage or the assignment or assumption of the same, including an assignment adjudged by the Tribal Court, or by operation of law, except as such merger may arise upon satisfaction of the Leasehold Mortgage.", "num": "4.09.100", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.09|4.09.100", "title": "4.09.100 No Merger of Estates", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.09.100"}
