{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 4.10.060 Effective Date, Severability and Repealer (a) Time of Taking Effect This Ordinance shall take effect on January 1, 2019. (b) Severability If any provision of this ordinance or application thereof to any person or circumstance is held invalid, the invalidity does not affect other provisions or applications of the ordinance that can be given effect without the invalid provision or application, and to this end the provisions of this Ordinance are severable. (c) Repealer Any other acts and parts of acts inconsistent with this Ordinance are hereby repealed. ( 5-15-18-1028 .) Prior Codifications \u00a74.10.060 was formerly codified as 427.6", "num": "4.10.060", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|4|4.10|4.10.060", "title": "4.10.060 Effective Date, Severability and Repealer", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/4.10.060"}
