{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 5.01.120 Classification Modifying Games (a) Modification of Gaming Systems (1) The GM shall submit to the Tribal Gaming Commission a request for a review of a Gaming System that is to be modified by providing a detailed description of the modification and how the modification affects the Gaming System. If the Tribal Gaming Commission determines that the modification represents a material change to the classification of the Gaming System, the GM must submit an application pursuant to part (2) of this Section . (2) An application for a new Classification Determination shall not be required if the modification does not result in a material change to the operation of the Gaming System. (3) The Tribal Gaming Commission shall maintain a list of modifications determined by the Tribal Gaming Commission to be non-material, which shall be updated periodically by the Tribal Gaming Commission as technology advances. ( 9-21-12 ; 11-29-07-190 ; 11-29-07-189 ; 12-29-04-31 ; 12-29-04-30 ; 12-29-04-29 ; 3-21-03-59 ; 6-19-02-295 ; 9-18-01-157 ; 7-2-01-119B ; 3-01-01-49 ; 1-5-00-369 ; 4-8-98-132 ; 9-6-93-81 ; 10-7-92-154 ; 9-20-91-151 ; 4-1-87-39 ; 6-4-86-34 .) Prior Codifications \u00a75.01.120 was formerly codified as 500.34", "num": "5.01.120", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|5|5.01|B|5.01.120", "title": "5.01.120 Classification Modifying Games", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/5.01.120"}
