{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 5.08.010 Purpose The Tribal Council of the Bad River Band of Lake Superior Tribe of Chippewa Indians (hereinafter \"Tribe\"), empowered by the Bad River constitution to enact ordinances, hereby enacts this ordinance in order to set the terms for Class II and III gaming. ( 9-21-12 ; 11-29-07-190 ; 11-29-07-189 ; 12-29-04-31 ; 12-29-04-30 ; 12-29-04-29 ; 3-21-03-59 ; 6-19-02-295 ; 9-18-01-157 ; 7-2-01-119B ; 3-01-01-49 ; 1-5-00-369 ; 4-8-98-132 ; 9-6-93-81 ; 10-7-92-154 ; 9-20-91-151 ; 4-1-87-39 ; 6-4-86-34 .) Prior Codifications \u00a75.08.010 was formerly codified as 550.1", "num": "5.08.010", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|5|5.08|5.08.010", "title": "5.08.010 Purpose", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/5.08.010"}
