{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 5.08.020 Gaming Authorized Class II and III gaming as defined in the Indian Gaming Regulatory Act, P.L. 100-447, 25 U.S.C. Section 2703(7)(A) and (8)(IGRA) and by the regulations promulgated by the National Indian Gaming Commission at 25 C.F.R. sections 502.3 and 502.4 (as published in the Federal Register at 57 FR 12382-12393, April 9, 1992) is hereby authorized. ( 9-21-12 ; 11-29-07-190 ; 11-29-07-189 ; 12-29-04-31 ; 12-29-04-30 ; 12-29-04-29 ; 3-21-03-59 ; 6-19-02-295 ; 9-18-01-157 ; 7-2-01-119B ; 3-01-01-49 ; 1-5-00-369 ; 4-8-98-132 ; 9-6-93-81 ; 10-7-92-154 ; 9-20-91-151 ; 4-1-87-39 ; 6-4-86-34 .) Prior Codifications \u00a75.08.020 was formerly codified as 550.2", "num": "5.08.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|5|5.08|5.08.020", "title": "5.08.020 Gaming Authorized", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/5.08.020"}
