{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 5.08.030 Ownership of Gaming The Tribe shall have the sole propriety interest in and responsibility for the conduct of any gaming operation on the Bad River Reservation or authorized by this ordinance. ( 9-21-12 ; 11-29-07-190 ; 11-29-07-189 ; 12-29-04-31 ; 12-29-04-30 ; 12-29-04-29 ; 3-21-03-59 ; 6-19-02-295 ; 9-18-01-157 ; 7-2-01-119B ; 3-01-01-49 ; 1-5-00-369 ; 4-8-98-132 ; 9-6-93-81 ; 10-7-92-154 ; 9-20-91-151 ; 4-1-87-39 ; 6-4-86-34 .) Prior Codifications \u00a75.08.030 was formerly codified as 550.3", "num": "5.08.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|5|5.08|5.08.030", "title": "5.08.030 Ownership of Gaming", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/5.08.030"}
