{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 5.08.060 Protection of the Environment and Public Health and Safety Class II and III gaming facilities shall be constructed, maintained and operated in a manner that adequately protects the environment and the public health and safety. ( 9-21-12 ; 11-29-07-190 ; 11-29-07-189 ; 12-29-04-31 ; 12-29-04-30 ; 12-29-04-29 ; 3-21-03-59 ; 6-19-02-295 ; 9-18-01-157 ; 7-2-01-119B ; 3-01-01-49 ; 1-5-00-369 ; 4-8-98-132 ; 9-6-93-81 ; 10-7-92-154 ; 9-20-91-151 ; 4-1-87-39 ; 6-4-86-34 .) Prior Codifications \u00a75.08.060 was formerly codified as 550.6", "num": "5.08.060", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|5|5.08|5.08.060", "title": "5.08.060 Protection of the Environment and Public Health and Safety", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/5.08.060"}
