{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 6.01.020 Qualifications for Membership Committee Members Committee members shall meet the following qualifications: (a) Member of the Bad River Band of Lake Superior Tribe of Chippewa Indians; (b) At least 21 years of age; (c) Resident of the Bad River Reservation for at least one year prior to Committee membership and knowledge of the history of the Bad River Band; (d) Committee members shall not be Tribal Council members, Bad River Tribal Court judges, employees of the Enrollment Office, Legal Department or Tribal Court. ( 12-5-90-154 ; 6-1-83-39 ; 8-13-79-161 ; 8-28-78-19 .) Prior Codifications \u00a76.01.020 was formerly codified as 601.02", "num": "6.01.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|6|6.01|6.01.020", "title": "6.01.020 Qualifications for Membership Committee Members", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/6.01.020"}
