{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 8.01.020 Exclusive Remedy Exclusion and removal does not prevent, negate or exclude the use of any other remedy or penalty that is otherwise provided by this Code or other governing federal, state or tribal law. ( 8-14-02-324 .) Prior Codifications \u00a78.01.020 was formerly codified as 800.5", "num": "8.01.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|8|8.01|8.01.020", "title": "8.01.020 Exclusive Remedy", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/8.01.020"}
