{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 10.01.090 Penalties Any person who violates the provisions of this ordinance shall be subject to the following penalties: Any person violating a provision of \u00a71000.07 shall be required to forfeit $30.00 for a first offense, $45.00 for a second offense and $60.00 for a third or subsequent offense within a two year period. Prior Codifications \u00a710.01.090 was formerly codified as 1000.09", "num": "10.01.090", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|10|10.01|10.01.090", "title": "10.01.090 Penalties", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/10.01.090"}
