{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 10.02.080 Expenses/Stipends Members of the Police Commission are authorized reimbursements for costs associated with official Police Commission business and shall be paid reasonable stipends. The Tribal Council shall authorize a sufficient amount of funding to meet the budgeted needs of the Police Commission. ( 10-25-01-174 ; 11-6-91-160 .) Prior Codifications \u00a710.02.080 was formerly codified as 1001.8", "num": "10.02.080", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|10|10.02|10.02.080", "title": "10.02.080 Expenses/Stipends", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/10.02.080"}
