{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 10.02.090 Reports The Police Commission shall be invited to meet with the Tribal Council at least once per year and from time to time as necessary so as to report any information deemed important. ( 10-25-01-174 ; 11-6-91-160 .) Prior Codifications \u00a710.02.090 was formerly codified as 1001.9", "num": "10.02.090", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|10|10.02|10.02.090", "title": "10.02.090 Reports", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/10.02.090"}
