{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 11.01.010 Purpose The Bad River Tribal Council may authorize the Tribe to offer health and/or disability insurance, including at its option, opting into the State of Wisconsin's Worker's Compensation system, to all full time employees, as defined in the Bad River Personnel and Policy Manual, of the Bad River Tribe, including its enterprises. Prior Codifications \u00a711.01.010 was formerly codified as 1100.1", "num": "11.01.010", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|11|11.01|11.01.010", "title": "11.01.010 Purpose", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/11.01.010"}
