{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 11.01.080 Health Benefits The Tribal Council, in its discretion may contract with an insurance carrier or offer a self-insured health insurance benefit plan to its employees. The health insurance plan, if any, shall constitute the health benefit made available by the Band to employees for work related injuries, injured workers. Prior Codifications \u00a711.01.080 was formerly codified as 1100.8", "num": "11.01.080", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|11|11.01|11.01.080", "title": "11.01.080 Health Benefits", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/11.01.080"}
