{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 11.01.100 Earnings, Method of Computation The method of calculating disability payments shall be established by the Tribal Council and promulgated in the disability policy, if any, sponsored by the Band. Prior Codifications \u00a711.01.100 was formerly codified as 1100.10", "num": "11.01.100", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|11|11.01|11.01.100", "title": "11.01.100 Earnings, Method of Computation", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/11.01.100"}
