{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 11.01.130 Rules of Procedure; Transcripts (a) All testimony at any hearing held under this chapter shall be recorded by a recording machine. Prior Codifications \u00a711.01.130 was formerly codified as 1100.14", "num": "11.01.130", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|11|11.01|11.01.130", "title": "11.01.130 Rules of Procedure; Transcripts", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/11.01.130"}
