{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 11.01.300 Sovereign Immunity By enacting this ordinance the Tribe in no way waives its inherent sovereignty and with all rights and privileges, including but not limited to sovereign immunity. Prior Codifications \u00a711.01.300 was formerly codified as 1100.31", "num": "11.01.300", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|11|11.01|11.01.300", "title": "11.01.300 Sovereign Immunity", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/11.01.300"}
