{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 13.01.020 Purpose The Bad River Band seeks to encourage the formation of charitable organizations within the exterior boundaries of the Bad River Reservation its works both on and off the Bad River Reservation. By this ordinance the Bad River Band authorizes the charter and regulation of charitable organizations. ( 5-30-02-285 .) Prior Codifications \u00a713.01.020 was formerly codified as 1300.2", "num": "13.01.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|13|13.01|13.01.020", "title": "13.01.020 Purpose", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/13.01.020"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/13.01.030", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 13.01.030 Scope The chartering of charitable organizations applies to specifically designated tribally sanctioned non-profit operations and/or enterprises subordinate to the Bad River Tribal Government. ( 5-30-02-285 .) Prior Codifications \u00a713.01.030 was formerly codified as 1300.3", "num": "13.01.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|13|13.01|13.01.030", "title": "13.01.030 Scope", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/13.01.030"}
