{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 13.01.050 Severability If any portion of this ordinance is found to be invalid for any reason, the remaining portions of this ordinance shall remain in effect. ( 5-30-02-285 .) Prior Codifications \u00a713.01.050 was formerly codified as 1300.5", "num": "13.01.050", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|13|13.01|13.01.050", "title": "13.01.050 Severability", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/13.01.050"}
