{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 13.01.130 Name The chartered organization shall include the phrase \"Non-Profit Business Organization Chartered by the Bad River Band\" in it logo and letterhead. ( 5-30-02-285 .) Prior Codifications \u00a713.01.130 was formerly codified as 1300.13", "num": "13.01.130", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|13|13.01|13.01.130", "title": "13.01.130 Name", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/13.01.130"}
