{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 15.01.690 Reservation of Right The Bad River Tribal Council hereby reserves the right to alter, amend or increase or decrease the fees, forfeiture and penalties imposed herein, amend or repeal the several provisions of this Ordinance, and all rights and privileges granted or extended hereunder shall be subject to such reserved right. Prior Codifications \u00a715.01.690 was formerly codified as 1500.61", "num": "15.01.690", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|15|15.01|15.01.690", "title": "15.01.690 Reservation of Right", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/15.01.690"}
