{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 15.01.700 Revenue Distribution All revenue derived from fees imposed by this Ordinance shall be deposited in the general revenue account of the Bad River Band. Prior Codifications \u00a715.01.700 was formerly codified as 1500.62", "num": "15.01.700", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|15|15.01|15.01.700", "title": "15.01.700 Revenue Distribution", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/15.01.700"}
