{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 16.01.100 Penalties Violation of this ordinance shall carry a forfeiture of not more than $50.00 for the first offense; $100.00 for the Second offense within 3 years of the first offense; and $500.00 per incident, for three or more offenses within 3 years of the first offense. Violators are also subject to immediate confiscation of all fireworks in the immediate possession of the violator or violators. Prior Codifications \u00a716.01.100 was formerly codified as 1600.10", "num": "16.01.100", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|16|16.01|16.01.100", "title": "16.01.100 Penalties", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/16.01.100"}
