{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 17.01.010 Purpose The purpose behind the creation of a Tribal Repatriation Committee is to appoint a body of individuals to directly engage in activities designed to locate, inventory and repatriate human remains, funerary objects, sacred objects and objects of cultural patrimony which should rightfully be repatriated to the Bad River Band of Lake Superior Tribe of Chippewa Indians and which are currently being held in museums, educational institutions, and other agencies, offices or locations. Prior Codifications \u00a717.01.010 was formerly codified as 1700.1", "num": "17.01.010", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|17|17.01|17.01.010", "title": "17.01.010 Purpose", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/17.01.010"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/17.01.020", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 17.01.020 Scope This ordinance is applicable to Bad River Repatriation Committee as it relates to the Bad River Band's repatriation activities and efforts. Prior Codifications \u00a717.01.020 was formerly codified as 1700.2", "num": "17.01.020", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|17|17.01|17.01.020", "title": "17.01.020 Scope", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/17.01.020"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/17.01.030", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code. 17.01.030 Authority This ordinance is enacted pursuant to Article VI, Section 1(m) and 1(n) of the Constitution and Bylaws of the Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Tribe of Chippewa Indians. Prior Codifications \u00a717.01.030 was formerly codified as 1700.3", "num": "17.01.030", "path": "library|Bad River Band of the Lake Superior Chippewa Indians Tribal Code|17|17.01|17.01.030", "title": "17.01.030 Authority", "url": "/us/nsn/badriver/council/code/17.01.030"}
